s_list
  #list(
    x-init='$store.header.title = "[##_list_conform_##]"'
    data-list-style='[##_list_style_##]')
    s_list_rep
      +index('list_rep')
    s_list_empty
      #empty(class='rounded-sm text-center p-6 text-h-800 dark:text-h-200 bg-h-200 dark:bg-h-700')
        .txt(class='text-lg font-bold') 게시글을 찾을 수 없습니다.
        .desc 검색어를 다시 입력하거나 다른 카테고리로 이동해보세요.

style
  :postcss
    #tt-body-index,
    #tt-body-category,
    #tt-body-tag,
    #tt-body-search {
      #global-header ~ .post,
      [data-list-style=gallery],
      [data-list-style=list],
      [data-list-style=grid],
      [data-list-style=zigzag] {
        @apply w-full px-4 lg:px-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-idx;
      }

      [data-list-style=slider] {
        @apply w-full h-screen;
      }

      [data-list-style=grid],
      [data-list-style=gallery] {
        @apply grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3;
      }

      [data-list-style=list],
      [data-list-style=zigzag] {
        @apply flex flex-col gap-y-6 sm:gap-y-0;
      }
    }

style
  :postcss
    #tt-body-index,
    #tt-body-category,
    #tt-body-tag,
    #tt-body-search {
      [data-list-style=grid] {
        @apply gap-4 lg:gap-8;
      }
    }

style
  :postcss
    #tt-body-index,
    #tt-body-category,
    #tt-body-tag,
    #tt-body-search {
      [data-list-style=gallery] {
        @apply gap-2;
      }
    }
